        "message": "Path Traversal in get_template\n\nThe get_template function joins user-controllable path input with TEMPLATES_LOCATION using os.path.join without validating that the resulting path stays within the templates directory. An attacker could use path traversal sequences (e.g., ../../etc/passwd) to read arbitrary files.\n\nImpact: An attacker can read arbitrary files on the filesystem by providing path traversal sequences.\n\nFix: Validate the resolved path using os.path.realpath() and ensure it starts with TEMPLATES_LOCATION before opening the file.",
